         <li class="- topic/li ">Ensure all the mandatory fields are filled.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Start date and End date must be the same across all sections.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Duplicate benefit lines must not be added.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Top bundle product must match the existing top bundle product.<note type="note" class="- topic/note ">If the above-mentioned conditions are not fulfilled, a validation error message appears for each benefit line on the Import Page. You need to contact the IT Support team if you get a warning message related to the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">UOM.</b>
